{"tid":873393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"員警隨身監視器爆炸　NYPD停用3,000鏡頭","createTime":"2018-10-23T11:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T12:07:09.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8bedfada6035924ff828d48bd25f1ed1ebb64658","tid":873393,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:49:32.000Z","msg":"紐約巿警察局周日證實，有員警身上的監視器發生爆炸，但無造成傷亡。當局已立刻回收近3,000個同款鏡頭。<br />\n <br />\n事發於上周六晚，一名員警在史丹頓島（Staten Island）巡邏期間，發現胸前的監視器突然冒煙，脫下後隨即起火爆炸。警方翌日證實事件，初步調查發現涉事的Vievu LE-5型號攝影機，內置電池發生爆炸，原因仍在調查中。<br />\n <br />\n目前，全紐約巿一共有近1.6萬名員警，佩戴隨身監視器巡邏。警方表示，已即時回收使用中的2,990個有問題型號鏡頭，強調以前線員警安全為重。至於其餘1.3萬多名員警，將繼續使用同一家公司生產、但不同型號的攝影機。"},{"pid":"3c753f07637a61ce7c641b72d8c218f93d679caa","tid":873393,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:55:22.000Z","msg":"是咪國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134e681dfe88d436d5b9b83e3ebb5ffce473c470","tid":873393,"uid":47296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c753f07637a61ce7c641b72d8c218f93d679caa","tid":873393,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:55:22.000Z","msg":"是咪國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"你國家？"},{"pid":"cb82b14f865fe88f81d4f1b21b4e141b6f1ea057","tid":873393,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"134e681dfe88d436d5b9b83e3ebb5ffce473c470","tid":873393,"uid":47296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c753f07637a61ce7c641b72d8c218f93d679caa","tid":873393,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:55:22.000Z","msg":"是咪國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"你國家？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"美國"},{"pid":"e03e54e338501ccc815d48652edf8ab30972c1db","tid":873393,"uid":23298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"監視器香左"}]}